1. Create new env python=3.7
2. Install gym-retro
3. Install Tensorflow==1.15
4. Clone and install OpenAI baselines: https://github.com/openai/baselines
5. Clone and install stable-baselines:
5. Integrate your game
6. Edit make_retro() call in retro.examples.ppo.py to include Contrib games
7. Edit retro.examples.ppo to wrap the environment in an instance of baselines.bench.Monitor
n. Run: python -m retro.examples.ppo --game <game-name>